data.description: Looking for your own homestead haven close to Lake Life?  Come see this charming 3 bed, 1 bath home on 0.65-acre located just ONE mile from the beautiful Norris Lake! Embrace country living that this property offers including a variety of fruit trees, thornless blackberry and raspberry bushes, and mini kiwi berry bushes for your harvest delight. Step inside this cozy cottage home which features updated ceilings in the kitchen and living room, ensuring modern comfort. The durable metal roof adds a touch of longevity to this idyllic haven. Outside you will find two outbuildings, one 20x14 workshop that is wired with electricity, along with a 10x13 storage shed. Be sure to note the inviting 18x18 above-ground pool, delightful outdoor fountain, along with a small fire pit area that invite a serene lifestyle enjoyment from the patio. Seize this opportunity to cultivate a fulfilling homestead lifestyle in this warm and welcoming cottage. Additional options abound with the opportunity to cultivate this home as a summertime getaway with its convenient location being only one mile away from Norris Lake. Buyer to verify all information and all measurements prior to making an informed offer.
